[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     34[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Suggested fix:** Either add a simple calibration step after the local model training in the "Putting It All Together" section (even a comment-only placeholder showing where it would go), or add an explicit inline comment in Step 3 noting: "The pseudocode includes a calibration step here. We omit it in this demo because the local GradientBoostingClassifier's predict_proba is already reasonably calibrated for synthetic data. In production with XGBoost, calibration is essential."
